info.title: Freight Unit (A2X)
info.description:
In addition, the following operations are possible:

* Report events

A freight unit is a set of goods that are transported together across the entire transportation chain.

x-sap-shortText: Update and cancel freight units using this synchronous inbound service

* Transportation Orders (TM_TRANSPORTATION_ORDER)
* Transportation Order: Items (TM_TRANSPORTATION_ORDER_ITEM)
* Transportation Order: Stages (TM_TRANSPORTATION_ORDER_STAGE)
